## The situation

Most businesses — agencies included — pay for a stack of marketing tools:

- Social media scheduling: $15-100/month
- SEO monitoring: $99-449/month
- Email marketing: $13-350/month
- Analytics dashboards: $0-100/month

That's $200-1,000/month just to manage your online presence. And you don't own any of it — stop paying and the tools disappear.

We asked: **what if we built these tools ourselves, on the same technology we use for client websites?**

## The problems we were solving

- **Too many logins**: Four different platforms with four different dashboards to manage social media alone
- **Expensive subscriptions**: $200+/month in SaaS fees for tools we used daily
- **No ownership**: If we stopped paying, our scheduling history, SEO data, and analytics disappeared
- **No integration**: Each tool worked in isolation — social scheduling didn't talk to SEO didn't talk to analytics

## What we built

### Social media scheduling

Write a post, pick which platforms to share it on (Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, Google Business Profile), schedule the date and time, and it goes out automatically. No switching between 4 different apps. No copy-pasting the same content into each platform manually.

### AI-assisted content creation

Describe what you want to say and get a draft in seconds. The AI understands the Upstate SC market and writes content tailored for local small businesses. Edit it, refine it, schedule it — what used to take 30 minutes takes 5.

### SEO management

Control how every page appears in Google search results — titles, descriptions, and structured data — without touching any code. See a preview of exactly what Google will show before making changes.

### Traffic analytics

See where your visitors are coming from, which pages they visit, and how your traffic is trending — all in one dashboard instead of switching between multiple tools.

## The results

- **One dashboard**: Social media, SEO, content, and analytics in one place
- **No subscriptions**: Replaced $200+/month in SaaS fees with tools we fully own
- **Full ownership**: All data stays with us — no vendor lock-in
- **AI-powered**: Content creation that used to take 30 minutes now takes 5

## How this benefits our clients

The tools we built for ourselves are the same tools we offer to clients:

- **Social media management**: We manage your presence, schedule posts, and track engagement across all platforms from one place
- **SEO monitoring**: We track how your pages perform in search and make adjustments to improve rankings
- **Traffic insights**: Clear reports on who's visiting your site and what's working
- **Content creation**: AI-assisted drafting helps us create more content, faster, without sacrificing quality

When you work with us on a Growth or Full Partner retainer plan, these are the tools powering your marketing.

## Why this matters for your business

We don't just build websites. We build the tools that make websites work harder — for ourselves and for our clients. Everything runs on modern, fast infrastructure that we fully own and control.

**No monthly subscriptions. No vendor lock-in. Full ownership.** That's the power of building custom.

